## Anomaly Detection

### Statistical Methods

| Method | Use Case | Threshold |
|--------|----------|-----------|
| Z-score | Numeric fields, normal distribution | abs(z) > 3 |
| IQR | Numeric fields, skewed distribution | < Q1 - 1.5*IQR or > Q3 + 1.5*IQR |
| Percentage change | Time series | > 50% change from previous period |
| Cardinality change | Categorical fields | > 20% change in unique values |

