## Data Contracts

### Contract Structure

```yaml
contract:
  name: user_events
  version: "1.2"
  owner: team-data
  sla:
    freshness: "1 hour"
    completeness: "99.5%"
  schema:
    - name: user_id
      type: string
      required: true
      unique: false
    - name: event_type
      type: string
      required: true
      allowed_values: ["click", "view", "purchase"]
    - name: timestamp
      type: timestamp
      required: true
  quality_rules:
    - rule: row_count
      min: 1000
      max: 1000000
    - rule: null_rate
      field: user_id
      max: 0.0
```

